{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "古者王公大人爲政於國家者，情欲譽之審，賞罰之當，刑政之不過失。", "text_normalized": "古者王公大人爲政於國家者，情欲譽之審，賞罰之當，刑政之不過失。", "canonical_ref": "18.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "「古者有語：", "text_normalized": "「古者有語：", "canonical_ref": "18.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "『謀而不得，則以往知來，以見知隱』。", "text_normalized": "『謀而不得，則以往知來，以見知隱』。", "canonical_ref": "18.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "」謀若此，可得而知矣。", "text_normalized": "」謀若此，可得而知矣。", "canonical_ref": "18.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "今師徒唯毋興起，冬行恐寒，夏行恐暑，此不可以冬夏爲者也。", "text_normalized": "今師徒唯毋興起，冬行恐寒，夏行恐暑，此不可以冬夏爲者也。", "canonical_ref": "18.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "春則廢民耕稼樹藝，秋則廢民穫斂。", "text_normalized": "春則廢民耕稼樹藝，秋則廢民穫斂。", "canonical_ref": "18.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "今唯毋廢一時，則百姓飢寒凍餒而死者，不可勝數。", "text_normalized": "今唯毋廢一時，則百姓飢寒凍餒而死者，不可勝數。", "canonical_ref": "18.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "今嘗計軍上，竹箭、羽旄、幄幕、甲、盾、撥、劫，往而靡弊腑冷不反者，不可勝數；", "text_normalized": "今嘗計軍上，竹箭、羽旄、幄幕、甲、盾、撥、劫，往而靡弊腑冷不反者，不可勝數；", "canonical_ref": "18.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "又與矛、戟、戈、劍、乘車，其列往碎折靡弊而不反者，不可勝數；", "text_normalized": "又與矛、戟、戈、劍、乘車，其列往碎折靡弊而不反者，不可勝數；", "canonical_ref": "18.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "與其牛馬肥而往、瘠而反，往死亡而不反者，不可勝數；", "text_normalized": "與其牛馬肥而往、瘠而反，往死亡而不反者，不可勝數；", "canonical_ref": "18.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "與其涂道之脩遠，糧食輟絕而不繼，百姓死者，不可勝數也；", "text_normalized": "與其涂道之脩遠，糧食輟絕而不繼，百姓死者，不可勝數也；", "canonical_ref": "18.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "與其居處之不安，食飲之不時，飢飽之不節，百姓之道疾病而死者，不可勝數。", "text_normalized": "與其居處之不安，食飲之不時，飢飽之不節，百姓之道疾病而死者，不可勝數。", "canonical_ref": "18.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "喪師多不可勝數，喪師盡不可勝計，則是鬼神之喪其主后，亦不可勝數。", "text_normalized": "喪師多不可勝數，喪師盡不可勝計，則是鬼神之喪其主后，亦不可勝數。", "canonical_ref": "18.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "國家發政，奪民之用、廢民之利，若此甚衆，然而何爲爲之？", "text_normalized": "國家發政，奪民之用、廢民之利，若此甚衆，然而何爲爲之？", "canonical_ref": "18.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "我貪伐勝之名，及得之利，故爲之。", "text_normalized": "我貪伐勝之名，及得之利，故爲之。", "canonical_ref": "18.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "計其所自勝，無所可用也。", "text_normalized": "計其所自勝，無所可用也。", "canonical_ref": "18.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "計其所得，反不如所喪者之多。", "text_normalized": "計其所得，反不如所喪者之多。", "canonical_ref": "18.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "今攻三里之城，七里之郭，攻此不用銳，且無殺而徒得，此然也。", "text_normalized": "今攻三里之城，七里之郭，攻此不用銳，且無殺而徒得，此然也。", "canonical_ref": "18.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "殺人多必數於萬，寡必數於千，然後三里之城、七里之郭且可得也。", "text_normalized": "殺人多必數於萬，寡必數於千，然後三里之城、七里之郭且可得也。", "canonical_ref": "18.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "今萬乘之國，虛數於千，不勝而入，廣衍數於萬，不勝而辟。", "text_normalized": "今萬乘之國，虛數於千，不勝而入，廣衍數於萬，不勝而辟。", "canonical_ref": "18.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "然則土地者，所有餘也；", "text_normalized": "然則土地者，所有餘也；", "canonical_ref": "18.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "王民者，所不足也。", "text_normalized": "王民者，所不足也。", "canonical_ref": "18.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "今盡王民之死，嚴下上之患，以爭虛城，則是棄所不足，而重所有餘也。", "text_normalized": "今盡王民之死，嚴下上之患，以爭虛城，則是棄所不足，而重所有餘也。", "canonical_ref": "18.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "爲政若此，非國之務者也。", "text_normalized": "爲政若此，非國之務者也。", "canonical_ref": "18.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "飾攻戰者也言曰：", "text_normalized": "飾攻戰者也言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "南則荊吳之王，北則齊晉之君，始封於天下之時，其土地之方，未至有數百里也；", "text_normalized": "南則荊吳之王，北則齊晉之君，始封於天下之時，其土地之方，未至有數百里也；", "canonical_ref": "18.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "人徒之衆，未至有數十萬人也。", "text_normalized": "人徒之衆，未至有數十萬人也。", "canonical_ref": "18.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "以攻戰之故，土地之博至有數千里也，人徒之衆至有數百萬人，故當攻戰而不可爲也。", "text_normalized": "以攻戰之故，土地之博至有數千里也，人徒之衆至有數百萬人，故當攻戰而不可爲也。", "canonical_ref": "18.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "雖四五國則得利焉，猶謂之非行道也。", "text_normalized": "雖四五國則得利焉，猶謂之非行道也。", "canonical_ref": "18.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "譬若醫之藥人之有病者然，今有醫於此，和合其祝藥之于天下之有病者而藥之，萬人食此，若醫四五人得利焉，猶謂之非行藥也。", "text_normalized": "譬若醫之藥人之有病者然，今有醫於此，和合其祝藥之于天下之有病者而藥之，萬人食此，若醫四五人得利焉，猶謂之非行藥也。", "canonical_ref": "18.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "故孝子不以食其親，忠臣不以食其君。", "text_normalized": "故孝子不以食其親，忠臣不以食其君。", "canonical_ref": "18.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "古者封國於天下，尚者以耳之所聞，近者以目之所見，以攻戰亡者不可勝數。", "text_normalized": "古者封國於天下，尚者以耳之所聞，近者以目之所見，以攻戰亡者不可勝數。", "canonical_ref": "18.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "何以知其然也？", "text_normalized": "何以知其然也？", "canonical_ref": "18.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "東方有莒之國者，其爲國甚小，閒於大國之閒，不敬事於大，大國亦弗之從而愛利。", "text_normalized": "東方有莒之國者，其爲國甚小，閒於大國之閒，不敬事於大，大國亦弗之從而愛利。", "canonical_ref": "18.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "是以東者越人夾削其壤地，西者齊人兼而有之。", "text_normalized": "是以東者越人夾削其壤地，西者齊人兼而有之。", "canonical_ref": "18.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "計莒之所以亡於齊越之閒者，以是攻戰也。", "text_normalized": "計莒之所以亡於齊越之閒者，以是攻戰也。", "canonical_ref": "18.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "雖南者陳蔡，其所以亡於吳越之閒者，亦以攻戰。", "text_normalized": "雖南者陳蔡，其所以亡於吳越之閒者，亦以攻戰。", "canonical_ref": "18.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "雖北者且不一著何，其所以亡於燕代胡貊之閒者，亦以攻戰也。", "text_normalized": "雖北者且不一著何，其所以亡於燕代胡貊之閒者，亦以攻戰也。", "canonical_ref": "18.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "是故子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "「古者王公大人，情欲得而惡失，欲安而惡危，故當攻戰而不可不非。", "text_normalized": "「古者王公大人，情欲得而惡失，欲安而惡危，故當攻戰而不可不非。", "canonical_ref": "18.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "18.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "飾攻戰者之言曰：", "text_normalized": "飾攻戰者之言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "彼不能收用彼衆，是故亡。", "text_normalized": "彼不能收用彼衆，是故亡。", "canonical_ref": "18.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "我能收用我衆，以此攻戰於天下，誰敢不賓服哉？", "text_normalized": "我能收用我衆，以此攻戰於天下，誰敢不賓服哉？", "canonical_ref": "18.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "子雖能收用子之衆，子豈若古者吳闔閭哉？", "text_normalized": "子雖能收用子之衆，子豈若古者吳闔閭哉？", "canonical_ref": "18.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "古者吳闔閭教七年，奉甲執兵，奔三百里而舍焉，次注林，出於冥隘之徑，戰於柏舉，中楚國而朝宋與及魯。", "text_normalized": "古者吳闔閭教七年，奉甲執兵，奔三百里而舍焉，次注林，出於冥隘之徑，戰於柏舉，中楚國而朝宋與及魯。", "canonical_ref": "18.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "至夫差之身，北而攻齊，舍於汶上，戰於艾陵，大敗齊人而葆之大山。", "text_normalized": "至夫差之身，北而攻齊，舍於汶上，戰於艾陵，大敗齊人而葆之大山。", "canonical_ref": "18.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "東而攻越，濟三江五湖，而葆之會稽。", "text_normalized": "東而攻越，濟三江五湖，而葆之會稽。", "canonical_ref": "18.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "九夷之國莫不賓服。", "text_normalized": "九夷之國莫不賓服。", "canonical_ref": "18.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "於是退不能賞孤，施舍羣萌，自恃其力，伐其攻，譽其智，怠於教，遂築姑蘇之臺，七年不成。", "text_normalized": "於是退不能賞孤，施舍羣萌，自恃其力，伐其攻，譽其智，怠於教，遂築姑蘇之臺，七年不成。", "canonical_ref": "18.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "及若此，則吳有離罷之心。", "text_normalized": "及若此，則吳有離罷之心。", "canonical_ref": "18.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "越王句踐視吳上下不相得，收其衆以復其讐。", "text_normalized": "越王句踐視吳上下不相得，收其衆以復其讐。", "canonical_ref": "18.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "入北郭，徙大內，圍王宮，而吳國以亡。", "text_normalized": "入北郭，徙大內，圍王宮，而吳國以亡。", "canonical_ref": "18.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "昔者晉有六將軍，而智伯莫爲強焉。", "text_normalized": "昔者晉有六將軍，而智伯莫爲強焉。", "canonical_ref": "18.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "計其土地之博，人徒之衆，欲以抗諸侯，以爲英名。", "text_normalized": "計其土地之博，人徒之衆，欲以抗諸侯，以爲英名。", "canonical_ref": "18.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "攻戰之速，故差論其爪牙之士，皆列其舟車之衆，以攻中行氏而有之。", "text_normalized": "攻戰之速，故差論其爪牙之士，皆列其舟車之衆，以攻中行氏而有之。", "canonical_ref": "18.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "以其謀爲旣已足矣，又攻茲范氏而大敗之。", "text_normalized": "以其謀爲旣已足矣，又攻茲范氏而大敗之。", "canonical_ref": "18.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "并三家以爲一家而不止，又圍趙襄子於晉陽。", "text_normalized": "并三家以爲一家而不止，又圍趙襄子於晉陽。", "canonical_ref": "18.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "及若此，則韓魏亦相從而謀曰：", "text_normalized": "及若此，則韓魏亦相從而謀曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "「古者有語：", "text_normalized": "「古者有語：", "canonical_ref": "18.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "『脣亡則齒寒。", "text_normalized": "『脣亡則齒寒。", "canonical_ref": "18.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "』趙氏朝亡，我夕從之；", "text_normalized": "』趙氏朝亡，我夕從之；", "canonical_ref": "18.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "趙氏夕亡，我朝從之。", "text_normalized": "趙氏夕亡，我朝從之。", "canonical_ref": "18.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "詩曰：", "text_normalized": "詩曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "『魚水不務，陸將何及乎？", "text_normalized": "『魚水不務，陸將何及乎？", "canonical_ref": "18.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "』」是以三主之君一心戮力，辟門除道，奉甲興士，韓魏自外，趙氏自內，擊智伯，大敗之。", "text_normalized": "』」是以三主之君一心戮力，辟門除道，奉甲興士，韓魏自外，趙氏自內，擊智伯，大敗之。", "canonical_ref": "18.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "是故子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "18.73", "notes": ""}
