{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "「君子不鏡於水，而鏡於人。", "text_normalized": "「君子不鏡於水，而鏡於人。", "canonical_ref": "18.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "鏡於水見面之容，鏡於人則知吉與凶。", "text_normalized": "鏡於水見面之容，鏡於人則知吉與凶。", "canonical_ref": "18.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "」今以功戰爲利，則蓋嘗鑒之於智伯之事乎？", "text_normalized": "」今以功戰爲利，則蓋嘗鑒之於智伯之事乎？", "canonical_ref": "18.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii", "source_id": "mozi-018-condemnation-of-offensive-war-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "此其爲不吉而凶，旣可得而知矣。", "text_normalized": "此其爲不吉而凶，旣可得而知矣。", "canonical_ref": "18.78", "notes": ""}
